songs.title: Mind Right
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Yeah, what?
What's up?

[Verse 1]
It's war time on everybody, po-po's, they can get it too
Trappin' 'round in the hood
I'm ridin' 'round with nothin' to do
Tried to give you some real talk, this here for my lil one
Never take a day off of grindin' up for my lil ones
I just know I'm flashy, fly as fuck and I'm gettin' it
Pittsburgh by Bali's, Pittsburgh by Fendi
Benzo and kizzo, my kinfolk go nympho
When they grippin' on that chopper
Grippin' on that yopper, woah
I came in the game with pain, struggle, frustration
I'm seeing the way you act, niggas betrayed me
You do whatever you want, but never betray me
I walk through the [?], it got me faded
I'm sippin' on lean like Goose, I know it's dangerous
I'm on good medication and I'm famous
Everything you explainin' is complicated
Money, power, more power, no conversation

[Chorus]
Let me at the door [?] just need to get my mind right
Smokin' on the kush every day, it get my mind right
Drinkin' on codeine, I just gotta get my mind right
I'm going' through some things, man I gotta get my mind right

[Post-Chorus]
Got a few racks on me stacked the long way
Got a extendo drum on the mac, it's on, baby
Take this bottle of Ace of Spades to your dome, baby
Take this bottle of Lortab's and have some fun, baby

[Verse 2]
(Instrumental)

[Chorus]
Let me at the door [?] just need to get my mind right
Smokin' on the kush every day, it get my mind right
Drinkin' on codeine, I just gotta get my mind right
I'm going' through some things, man I gotta get my mind right

[Post-Chorus]
Got a few racks on me stacked the long way
Got a extendo drum on the mac, it's on, baby
Take this bottle of Ace of Spades to your dome, baby
Take this bottle of Lortab's and have some fun, baby

[Verse 3]
(Instrumental)

[Chorus]

Smokin' on the kush every day, it get my mind right
Drinkin' on codeine, I just gotta get my mind right
I'm going' through some things, man I gotta get my mind right
